備註 Remarks
課程描述：
透過有價證券對公開發行的程序與買賣的討論，引領出關於有價證券的定義，買賣交易，證券商與證券交易，集中市場的相關規範，以期作為下學期進一步討論有價證券的公開收購、操縱市場、短線交易與歸入權、內線交易、利益輸送及反詐欺條款的相關議題之基礎，使學生能對證券交易法有一個完整的認識。
 
Course Description: The course discusses fundamental principles of securities regulation.  Various topics such as IPO, primary and secondary distributions, private placement, and proxy solicitation will be explored and discussed to serve as a solid basis for the advanced discussions of tender offer, manipulations, short swing rule and disgorgement right, insider trading, tunneling, and anti-fraud provisions in the next semester to enable students to gain acquaintance with securities regulation.

授課語言：   中文




